data.title: Jane Moore
data.meta_description: Jane Moore. Writer: The Ex Games. Jane Moore was born on 17 May 1962 in Oxford, Oxfordshire, England, UK. She is an actress and writer, known for The Ex Games, Annually Retentive (2006) and Have I Got News for You (1990). She has been married to Gary Farrow since 4 May 2002.
data.text:
A well-known British journalist, who writes on women's issues. She works for The Sun newspaper and has a weekly column, as well as being editor of the paper's women's issues and supplements.

[in 2017] I wish I'd slept with more men. I was very monogamous and I was very sort of like "Well, obviously I'm not going to entertain you at all unless we've been dating for at least three months", and now I just think "Why? Why not just lighten up a bit?" Probably I would have just been a little less uptight about that kind of thing.
